    /// @dev    This method is called only by authorized entities
    /// @param  token It could be 0xeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeeee
    ///         to recover locked native ETH or token compatible with ERC20 or ERC6909.
